e Beauty'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Beauty']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'White Bouquet'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Bouquet']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'White Cloud'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Cloud']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'White Delight'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Delight']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'White Harlequin'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Harlequin']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'White Perfection'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Perfection']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'White Profusion'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Profusion']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'White Spear'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Spear']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'White Spread'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Spread']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'White Queen'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Queen']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'White Wings'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'White Wings']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'Widecombe'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'Widecombe']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'Windy Hill'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'Windy Hill']]\n* [[Buddleja davidii 'Wine'|''Buddleja davidii'' 'Wine']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Ellen's Blue'|''Buddleja'' 'Ellen's Blue']]\n* [[Buddleja fallowiana 'AGS China Expedition'|''Buddleja fallowiana'' 'AGS China Expedition']]\n* [[Buddleja fallowiana 'Bishop's Violet'|''Buddleja fallowiana'' 'Bishop's Violet']]\n* [[Buddleja \u00d7 farquharii|''Buddleja'' \u00d7 ''farquharii'']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Flower Power'|''Buddleja'' 'Flower Power']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Colour Fountain Blue'|''Buddleja'' 'Foot Long']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Glasnevin'|''Buddleja'' 'Glasnevin']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Glass Slippers'|''Buddleja'' 'Glass Slippers']]\n* [[Buddleja globosa 'Cally Orange'|''Buddleja globosa'' 'Cally Orange']]\n* [[Buddleja globosa 'Cannington Gold'|''Buddleja globosa'' 'Cannington Gold']]\n* [[Buddleja globosa 'Danmark'|''Buddleja globosa'' 'Danmark']]\n* [[Buddleja globosa 'HCM98017'|''Buddleja globosa'' 'HCM98017']]\n* [[Buddleja globosa 'Lemon Ball'|''Buddleja globosa'' 'Lemon Ball']]\n* [[Buddleja globosa 'Los Lagos'|''Buddleja globosa'' 'Los Lagos']]\n* [[Bud