hus glabratus]]'' <small>(Spreng.) K.Schum.</small> (as ''B. glabrata'' <small>Spreng.</small>)\n\n==Gallery==\n<gallery>\nImage:Buddavii.jpg|''B. davidii'' - Invasive species, here in an urban area\nImage:Buddleja asiatica.jpg|''Buddleja madagascariensis'' - flowers and foliage\nFile:Ibuddleiaigarata.jpg|Unidentified ''Buddleja'' species in Igarata, Brazil\nFile:Monarch Butterfly Flower.jpg|Monarch butterfly feeding on ''Buddleja davidii'' in [[Connecticut]]\nFile:Buddleja officinalis with Red Admiral.jpg|[[Vanessa atalanta|Red Admiral]] butterfly feeding on ''Buddleja officinalis'' in January\n</gallery>\n\n==List of Buddleja cultivars and artificial hybrids==\nA large number of hybrids and cultivars, predominantly of ''B. davidii'', has been raised in nurseries on both sides of the Atlantic:\n{|\n|- valign=top\n|\n* [[Buddleja alternifolia 'Argentea'|''Buddleja alternifolia'' 'Argentea']]\n* [[Buddleja alternifolia 'Pmoore12'|''Buddleja alternifolia'' 'Pmoore12' = {{tdes|unique|caps}}]]\n* [[Buddleja asiatica 'Sweet Promise'|''Buddleja asiatica'' 'Sweet Promise']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Asian Moon'|''Buddleja'' 'Asian Moon']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Attraction'|''Buddleja'' 'Attraction']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Autumn Delight'|''Buddleja'' 'Autumn Delight']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Autumn Surprise'|''Buddleja'' 'Autumn Surprise']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Beech Park'|''Buddleja'' 'Beech Park']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Bel Argent'|''Buddleja'' 'Bel Argent']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Blaze Pink'|''Buddleja'' 'Blaze Pink']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Blizzard'|''Buddleja'' 'Blizzard']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Blue Chip'|''Buddleja'' 'Blue Chip']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Blue Chip Jr'|''Buddleja'' 'Blue Chip Jr']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Blue Gown'|''Buddleja'' 'Blue Gown']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Blue Trerice'|''Buddleja'' 'Blue Trerice']]\n* [[Buddleja 'Boscranz'|''Buddleja'' 'Boscranz' = {{tdes|Reve de Papillon Red|caps}}]]\n* [[Buddleja 'Bosjerry'|''Buddleja'' 'Bosjerry' = {{tdes|Reve de Papillon Lavender|caps}}]]\n* [[Buddleja 'Boy Blue'|''Buddleja'' 'Boy Blue']]\n* [[B